snippet.title: Gord | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Gord is an upcoming adventure strategy game set in a grim fantasy world inspired by Slavic folklore. Venture deep into forbidden lands, complete quests, and guide the fate of the Tribe of the Dawn.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1351210/Gord/

Join our Discord:
http://discord.gg/gordthegame

Follow us:
https://twitter.com/GordTheGame
https://www.instagram.com/gordthegame
https://www.facebook.com/GordTheGame

Find more info on our websites:
https://gord.game/
http://www.covenant.dev
